yamadonga ( english : thief yama ) is a 2007 telugu fantasy-action comedy film directed by s.s. rajamouli and produced by urmila gangaraju and p. chiranjeevi .   the film stars mohan babu , jr . ntr , priyamani and mamta mohandas in the lead roles .   the film released worldwide on 15 august 2007 .   upon release , the film was a critical and box office success .   it was also dubbed into hindi as lok parlok .